x=c(1,2,3,7,8,9,15)
dim(x)=c(7,1)
d=dist(x)

hc1=hclust(d,"single");
hc2=hclust(d,"complete");
hc3=hclust(d,"median");
hc4=hclust(d,"average");
plot(hc1)

plot(hc2)

plot(hc3)

plot(hc4)

opar=par(mfrow=c(2,2))
plot(hc1,hang=-1);
plot(hc2,hang=-1);
plot(hc3,hang=-1);
plot(hc4,hang=-1);

par(opar)

plot(hc1);re=rect.hclust(hc1,k=2)

plot(hc1);re=rect.hclust(hc1,k=3)
